## 📢 About This HTML Course

This repository is designed for beginners who want to learn HTML from scratch.

🧠 Each file in this course explains one important HTML tag or concept with simple, clean code.

💡 Ideal for:
- Students learning web development
- Self-learners starting HTML
- Anyone who wants to revise HTML basics with examples

📂 All code files are well-organized and easy to understand. Feel free to download, modify, and experiment.

✅ No external setup required — just open the files in your browser or any code editor like VS Code.

---

Thanks for visiting! 🌟  
If you find this helpful, don’t forget to ⭐ star the repository.
